data.name: GETALL_LIMIT_SQL
data.value:
with RESULT0 as ( select [CounterParty].Id as CounterPartyIdTo, [CounterParty].Shortname as ShortnameTo, [Country].Country as CountryTo, sum(isnull([Allocation].SublimitAmountInUSD2,0)) as SublimitAmountInUSDTo, SubLimitTypeTo.Id as SubLimitTypeIdTo, isnull(SubLimitTypeTo.Mnemonic,'') as SubLimitTypeTo from [Allocation]
left join [SystemStatus] on [SystemStatus].Id = [Allocation].AllocationSystemStatusId
left join [Status] on [Status].Id = [Allocation].StatusCodeId
left join [StatusCodes] on [StatusCodes].Id = [Status].StatusCodeId
left join [CounterParty] on [CounterParty].Id = [Allocation].CounterpartyId
left join [Country] on [Country].Id = [CounterParty].CountryId1
left join [SubLimitType] as SubLimitTypeTo on SubLimitTypeTo.Id = Allocation.SublimitTypeId2
where [StatusCodes].Id = 107 --Active and [SystemStatus].Id in (31,38) --and [CounterParty].Id = 1727
group by [CounterParty].Id, [CounterParty].Shortname, [Country].Country, SubLimitTypeTo.Id, SubLimitTypeTo.Mnemonic
),RESULT1 as ( select [CounterParty].Id as CounterPartyIdFrom, [CounterParty].Shortname as ShortnameFrom, [Country].Country as CountryFrom, sum(isnull([Allocation].SublimitAmountInUSD,0)) as SublimitAmountInUSDFrom, SubLimitTypeFrom.Id as SubLimitTypeIdFrom, isnull(SubLimitTypeFrom.Mnemonic,'') as SubLimitTypeFrom from [Allocation]
left join [SystemStatus] on [SystemStatus].Id = [Allocation].AllocationSystemStatusId
left join [Status] on [Status].Id = [Allocation].StatusCodeId
left join [StatusCodes] on [StatusCodes].Id = [Status].StatusCodeId
left join [CounterParty] on [CounterParty].Id = [Allocation].CounterpartyId
left join [Country] on [Country].Id = [CounterParty].CountryId1
left join [SubLimitType] as SubLimitTypeFrom on SubLimitTypeFrom.Id = Allocation.SublimitTypeId1
where [StatusCodes].Id = 107 --Active and [SystemStatus].Id in (31,38)
group by [CounterParty].Id, [CounterParty].Shortname, [Country].Country, SubLimitTypeFrom.Id, SubLimitTypeFrom.Mnemonic
) select *, (RESULT0.SublimitAmountInUSDTo - RESULT1.SublimitAmountInUSDFrom) as FinalLimit from RESULT0
left join RESULT1 on RESULT1.ShortnameFrom = RESULT0.ShortnameTo and RESULT1.SubLimitTypeFrom = RESULT0.SubLimitTypeTo
order by RESULT0.ShortnameTo --,RESULT0.SubLimitTypeTo --,RESULT1.SubLimitTypeFrom
